snippet.title: Corvette Z06 vs Lotus Emira // DRAG RACE, REVIEW & LAP TIMES
snippet.description:
What happens when you take the Car of the Year from last year and put it up against the previous year? You get a clash of extreme car enthusiasm. The Lotus Emira, our previous THCOTY, is a six figure, manual, supercharged Beauty. But the Z06 is a 670hp V8 Beast. Will they fight, or will they live in a castle forever under the sun? Let's find out in this video where we drag them, track them and give them some laptimes.

A huge thank you to Leggat Auto Group for letting us feature their Corvette! https://www.leggat.ca/?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=throttlehouse

And to the Emira owner, @AKMT.auto for letting us experience, even for a short while, what it would have been like to own an Emira.

Editor: Karston Chong
Sound: Harrison Dickson and Karston Chong

snippet.description:
#unity #luxurycar #luxuryvan #vans

Unity Leisure Travel Van 2024 Review | Ultimate Luxury and Performance on the Road

Discover the Unity Leisure Travel Van 2024, a perfect blend of luxury, performance, and practicality. Built on the Mercedes-Benz Sprinter chassis, this travel van offers multiple layout options, including Murphy Bed, Twin Beds, and Rear Lounge, each designed for maximum comfort and convenience. With a powerful 3.0L V6 turbo diesel engine, advanced safety features, and impressive fuel efficiency, the Unity ensures a smooth and reliable drive. Enjoy the sleek exterior design, panoramic windows, and high-end interior finishes that create a home-like feel on the road. Eco-friendly features like a solar panel system and energy-efficient appliances, along with modern technology integration, make this van a top choice for eco-conscious travelers. Experience the ultimate in travel comfort and style with the Unity Leisure Travel Van 2024. Perfect for road trips and adventures, this van promises a luxurious and enjoyable journey every time.

snippet.title: Никто не хотел браться. BMW 7 не заводится. При диагностике каждый раз разные ошибки.
snippet.description: На диагностику и ремонт привезли BMW седьмой серии на эвакуаторе. Жалобы на то что машина сначала начала глохнуть, но заводилась. В итоге и вовсе перестала заводиться. Первоначальная диагностика от владельца машины показала ошибки блоки двигателя, а именно ошибки по внутреннему напряжению блока двигателя и ещё несколько разных ошибок связанных с давлением во впускном коллекторе и дроссельной заслонки а также клапаном вентиляции бака. Диагностика при помощи сканера Launch, diazone, Кингболен Едиаг, диагзон, Ediag, Kingbolen показала наличие несколько ошибок причём при обнулении и чтение заново каждый раз ошибки были разные, а именно 2B9D 2A6C 2A19 2B9C 2CF0 2CEF A3AD A3AF . При первоначальной проверке машина завелась, но двигатель трясся. При попытке прогреть двигатель, автомобиль заглох, но снова завёлся, потом снова заглох и стартер крутил но двигатель Не запускался. При продолжении прогрева, двигатель заглох, стартер больше не крутил, и блок двигателя перестал выходить на связь. При дальнейшей диагностики обнаружилось что неисправность непосредственно в блоке двигателя. Снятие разбор и ремонт блока управления двигателем BMW седьмой серии е66.

snippet.title: Почему стоит купить 2024 Toyota Land Cruiser First Edition: обзор и тест-драйв | Новый Ленд Крузер
snippet.description:
Представляем обзор Toyota Land Cruiser 2024 года! Легендарный внедорожник вернулся на американский рынок полностью обновленным. В ролике мы расскажем об истории Toyota Land Cruiser, вы увидите эволюцию популярного SUV, который приобрел новый внешний вид, современные технологии и гибридный двигатель 2.4 i-Force Max. Мы покажем все нововведения и особенности 2024 Toyota Land Cruiser First Edition, к примеру, уникальные фары, противотуманки Rigid и новый дизайн экстерьера, который напоминает популярный в США FJ Cruiser. Внутри просторный салон, комфортные сиденья и вместительный багажник, идеально подходящий для семейных поездок и приключений. Проведем подробный тест-драйв Toyota Land Cruiser First Edition, покажем все режимы вождения и off-road функции, а также расскажем, как работает система Crawl Cruise Control. Смотрите полный обзор новой Toyota Land Cruiser и будьте в курсе всех деталей и характеристик этого замечательного внедорожника.

О нас: Более 20 лет компания Autobazar.Us (Автобазар ЮС) помогает людям осуществлять процесс покупки транспорта с американского рынка. Мы стараемся сделать процесс покупки авто из США для наших клиентов максимально легким, выгодным и быстрым.
80% нашего бизнеса – это экспорт новых автомобилей из США, которые не представлены на других рынках.  Кроме поставок новых автомобилей из США, мы предоставляем нашим клиентам возможность приобрести поддержанные авто с аукционов Манхейм (Manheim) и Адеса (Adesa). Так же имеем огромный опыт покупки аварийных автомобилей.  Мы зарегистрированы на всех крупнейших страховых аукционах - Copart (Копарт), IAAI (Авто иншуренс), Тотал Ресурс.  
• Все автомобили представленные на нашем сайте autobazar.us - это автомобили принадлежащие нашей компании или нашим клиентам, снятые на нашей площадке. Мы не продаем чужие авто и не выставляем фото с различных авто порталов
• Мы всегда покупаем автомобили за свои средства. Клиент оплачивает конечную стоимость автомобиля, только после получения подробных фото с нашей площадки и предоставления копии тех паспорта, на котором мы указаны владельцем авто.
• Все транзакции с нашей компанией осуществляются через банк. 
• Кроме экспорта автомобилей, мы так же продаем авто на внутреннем рынке США. 
• Мы много лет сотрудничаем с брокерами во всех основных портах отправки автомобилей, наши представители помогают клиентам проходить таможню (растаможка авто) "под ключ".

localized.title: Why you should buy the 2024 Toyota Land Cruiser First Edition: review and test drive
localized.description:
Introducing our 2024 Toyota Land Cruiser review! The legendary SUV has returned to the American market fully updated. In this video we will talk about the history of the Toyota Land Cruiser, you will see the evolution of the popular SUV, which has acquired a new appearance, modern technologies and a 2.4 i-Force Max hybrid engine. We will show all the innovations and features of the 2024 Toyota Land Cruiser First Edition, for example, unique headlights, Rigid fog lights and a new exterior design that reminds of the popular FJ Cruiser. Inside, there's a spacious cabin, comfortable seats and a spacious trunk, ideal for family trips and adventures. We will conduct a detailed test drive of the Toyota Land Cruiser First Edition, show you all the driving modes and off-road functions, and also show you how the Crawl Cruise Control system works. 80% of our business is the export of new cars from the United States that are not represented in other markets. In addition to supplying new cars from the USA, we provide our customers with the opportunity to purchase used cars from Manheim and Adesa auctions. We also have extensive experience in purchasing salvage vehicles. We are registered at all major insurance auctions - Copart (Copart), IAAI (Auto Insurance), Total Resource.
• All cars presented on our website autobazar.us are cars owned by our company or our clients, filmed on our site. We do not sell other people's cars and do not post photos from various auto portals.
• We always buy cars with our own funds. The client pays the final cost of the car only after receiving detailed photos from our site and providing a copy of the passport on which we are indicated as the owner of the car.
• All transactions with our company are carried out through the bank.
• In addition to exporting cars, we also sell cars in the US domestic market.
• We have been cooperating with brokers for many years in all major ports for sending cars; our representatives help clients go through customs (customs clearance of cars) on a turnkey basis.

snippet.title: Видео-дайджест 8 этапа/Video Digest Stage 8
snippet.description:
📍Грузовики: Вязович потерял более часа
Главным событием в зачёте грузовиков стали проблемы у действующего победителя ралли «Шелковый путь» в этом классе Сергея Вязовича. После прохождения трети дистанции на его автомобиле появились проблемы с рулевым управлением. С помощью товарищей по команде «МАЗ-СПОРТавто» Вязович смог починить грузовик, но уступил более часа и потерял лидерство в общем зачёте.

📍Мотовездеходы: Нифонтова во главе классификации
Андрей Новиков, лидировавший в общем зачёте перед восьмым этапом, столкнулся с техническими проблемами: отказал один из бензонасосов. Экипаж устранил неполадку за считанные минуты, однако на её поиск ушло много времени, и в итоге Новиков выбыл из тройки быстрейших экипажей в Т3.

📍Мотоциклы: Пуревдорж снова атакует
Мурун Пуревдорж, накануне столкнувшийся с проблемами, вновь атакует: райдер из Монголии отыграл у лидера общего зачёта Алексея Наумова 22 минуты. Однако после финиша Пуревдорж получил десять минут пенализации за нарушение правил проезда контрольной зоны и ещё десять секунд за превышение скорости. В итоге Мурун смог приблизиться к Наумову, но уступает ему более получаса.

Гранд тур и Хурэл морь
Для экипажей Гранд тура дистанция спецучастка на восьмом этапе составила 44 километра, после которого они отправились на финиш в деревню Баян-Уул для общей фотографии. Оттуда под конвоем караван внедорожников добрался до бивуака в городе Алтай, где участников ждал квест: нужно было найти скульптуру Хурэл морь — выполненную из бронзы статуэтку лошади, которая в Монголии считается священной. Таким образом, пилоты и штурманы не только получили дополнительную практику на бездорожье, но также ещё глубже познакомились с традициями и обычаями народов, по территориям которых проходит ралли «Шелковый путь».

snippet.title: Test Drive Lifted 1986 Chevrolet K10 4X4 SOLD Classic Car Addict
snippet.description:
Classic Car Addict is excited to present this apple red family owned 1986 Chevrolet K10 Silverado 4X4. This one is an instant standout the moment it arrives on the scene. And with proper V8 power, and a flawless paint, this lifted Chevy will bring all the heat. Red always looks good on the boxy lines of this generation Chevy truck. But this one likes to elevate the stock style.
That means a fresher respray to make sure you have a nice modern shine. The body has a quality style with nice panel alignment and doors that shut solid. This is highlighted further by the upgraded Silverado trim. Bright chrome bumpers and wide towing mirrors also add to the shine. And of course, the elevated style is taken literally with the taller 4x4 stance that's highlighted by the upgraded alloys and handy side steps. But let’s talk about that Rough Country 6 inch lift with FOX reservoir shocks. It also features the period correct rollbar with working five lights. And new LED lights all the way around. And the bed has beautiful golden oak wood with stainless trim.
The sea of red continues inside. They made nice investments in comfort like newer door panels, a smooth dash pad, and a comfy velour seat. There are also desirable features like the upgraded Pioneer AM/FM/CD stereo with aux input and remote, upgraded speakers, auxiliary readouts, tinted glass, and sliding rear glass. You also have provisions for cruise control, dual fuel tanks, and R134a air conditioning. It's built to be a good driver with details like the wraparound gauge panel, a tilt steering column, and the kind of stance that gives you a commanding view of the road.
Under the hood is Chevy's stout 350 cubic-inch V8 with roller cam with ZZ4 heads. We love upgrades, and so this one now inhales deeper with an Edelbrock four-barrel carburetor and an Edelbrock intake. And there's a nice V8 tune thanks to the dual exhaust and Flowmaster mufflers. 488 gears front and back, 19-bolt front axle, 12-bolt rear axle. Electric Holley fuel pump with dual fuel tanks. When you combine this kind of powerhouse with the two-speed 4x4 transfer case, newer off-road shocks, lifted stance, and deep tread tires, you have a true go-anywhere machine. The Automatic transmission not only gives you full control over the powerful V8, but also plenty of low-end torque right from the start. But we like this Chevy because it has a solid feeling on the road. And the power steering, power brakes, and front discs are there to make this classic truck a decent cruiser. The Chevy rolls on new 15 pro comp aluminum wheels and 35x10R15 BF Goodrich all terrain tires. One last thing, we’ve got dual batteries.
This is a classic Chevy truck that delivers both style and substance. That makes for a total package you need to get your hands on right now. This will be sold on a clean Arizona title. Call Classic Car Addict today at 480-256-1459.

snippet.title: Test Drive 1978 Chevrolet K10 4X4 Lifted SOLD Classic Car Addict
snippet.description:
Classic Car Addict is proud to present this awesome 1978 Chevrolet K10 stepside for sale in our Mesa, AZ showroom. In the past decade the C/K series of Chevrolet pickup trucks has really shot up in popularity. There are entire clubs and shows dedicated to purely this series of truck. Following the "Action Line" series Chevrolet introduced the "Rounded Line" series for the 3rd generation in 1973. This generation would later be referred to as "Square Bodies." The best part of being a K10 is that she’s got 4-wheel drive.
The cab features a black vinyl bench seat with yellow vinyl inserts as well as color-coordinated dash and door panels. The kick panels have been integrated with Kicker 6x9 speakers and a Highliner mounted headliner with integrated speakers and cab lighting. It features a Custom Sound Bluetooth radio with a Kicker bass knob. A four-spoke Lancer 400 steering wheel fronts the original instrument gauges consisting of a 100-mph speedometer, volts, oil pressure, temperature, and clock (the clock does not work). The six-digit odometer shows 97,820 miles, we cannot fully verify actual miles.
The truck is said to have been repainted in Yellow under current ownership. All chrome has been refinished on the K10 as well. The bed features Line X bedliner in black and the inside of the truck bed has been color matched to the yellow. She rolls on Goodyear MT/R Wrangler tires 35x12.50R15LT on chrome polished wheels with Super Wench locking hubs up front.
Under the hood is a rebuilt 350 V8 motor, consignor states that motor has an estimated 2,000 miles on it. The truck runs extremely well and is fitted with polished valve covers, Edelbrock intake, Edelbrock carburetor, long tube headers, polished alternator, electronic fuel pump, polished engine and transmission pan, rebuilt transfer case, power steering and power brakes (front disc). It features Pro Comp shocks with a lift height of 8 inches, and she rides beautifully. It sounds great through the Flowmaster rear dual exhaust.
This is a great looking truck that has a bunch of extras! Not only are these trucks popular, but it’s four-wheel drive! If you are looking for a vintage square body or a daily driver, this truck is ready to handle anything you throw at it. Call Classic Car Addict today at 480-256-1459. And be sure to check out our Instagram, YouTube, and Facebook pages to see 100+HD photos and videos.

snippet.title: I WILL get the engine out of my Truck... Eventually!
snippet.description:

snippet.title: How far can the CYBERTRUCK tow 11,000lbs in Freezing Weather?
snippet.description:
Today we have the brand new Tesla Cybertruck, and we'll be doing the hardest thing an EV Truck can do - Tow 11,000lbs in below freezing weather. How much can the Cybertruck tow? How far can the Cybertruck tow? Well today we find out the answer to both of those questions.

Tesla usually gives out some pretty nice perks when ordering through a referral code: https://ts.la/zack10701

This is a Dual Motor All Wheel Drive CyberTruck. The Vehicle was charged up to 100% the night before this test. (The Cybertruck Probably reached 100% around 2am in the morning, and then sat in my garage for about 6 hours or so while still plugged in, before coming out of the garage and being connected to the trailer. 

Watch the Rivian Towing video HERE: https://youtu.be/U8zDGN2Fdt4?si=V9O2EubPFyn4SVzW
Watch the Ford Lighting towing HERE: https://youtu.be/76l6lJhrgbc?si=NojC5JAcReN8jpuC
Watch my 600 mile road trip with @WHATSINSIDEFAMILY HERE:  https://youtu.be/clUvjo3xfzQ?si=sB0ZOTsFwcgWTrXi

And HUGE thanks to @OurCyberLife for letting us borrow his Cybertruck.

snippet.title: ABANDONED Ford F250 - First Drive On The HIGHWAY In 25 YEARS!
snippet.description:
This classic 1967 Ford F250 was saved off a property a year ago by my son and me.  It had been forgotten on a property by a farmer that had apparently given up on the truck.  We did get it running, but it had a host of issues to still work through that kept it off the road.  A year later, we're ready to get it on the road officially.  In this video, we'll be putting a complete brake system including all hard lines, soft lines, wheel cylinders, brake shoes, and even hardware, bearings, and seals. How do YOU think the first drive will go?

snippet.title: Built 131ci Twin Cam - PERFORMANCE CHOLO - all motor, all gas and loud as Fu*k
snippet.description:
John Tagley takes a Cholo styled 2002 Road King with an old twin cam 88ci and works side by side with Prestige Custom Cycles and their master tech "Panhead Andy" to design and build a 131 Twin Cam engine from the pre-existing H.D. case. The goal in mind was "as big as possible" combined with power-preserving mods to minimize parasitic losses to maximize performance on an unlikely chassis setup, thus creating what is now known as the "Performance Cholo", an entirely new concept of bike class.
With plenty of power now on tap, it was time to take it a step further and lighten the bike without compromising the Cholo look which proved to be a challenging task. The result is a machine that knows very few limitations in any aspect of the Harley Davidson world of bikes and will prove itself time and time again against much newer performance oriented bikes that compromised their looks for performance. All while retaining its "bike show worthy" aesthetic Cholo looks, and without falling victim to the dreaded stigma of "garage queen"

snippet.title: LAYFRAME CHOLO SOFTAIL - the long road to laying frame
snippet.description:
"Cholo John" makes his most extensive modification to what is now called, the LAYFRAME CHOLO SOFTAIL, the ultimate type of Cholo modded Softail. In this exclusive documentary the "hard to find information" on necessary LAYFRAME parts is spelled out and explained, the parts are installed and then tested in real world scenarios at 2 northeast motorcycle rallies, AMERICADE and the 99th annual LACONIA rally.
Overcoming real obstacles that builders would encounter during the process is detailed to shed light on how these typical problems can be solved by using some imagination and American perseverance.

snippet.title: CHOLO Road King - ALL NEW HYBRID CLASS from STYLE BLENDING
snippet.description:
This 2002 Road King classic was heading down the path to FULL CHOLO, when suddenly I decided to change course slightly. A hybrid build emerges from this 3rd round makeover to form a fresh look which is now proving its dominance on the streets with its undeniable bad boy presence, real world functionality and devastatingly loud pipes.
The new mods work together to aid in modernizing this 20 year old Harley and to spawn a blended build which utilizes looks and functionality from two separate classes. New mods include a full blended exhaust from S&S and Steady Custom Cycles, full air suspension and raked neck kit from American Suspension, 26/18 wheels by MetalSport, Apes, rear crash bars and bag guards once again by SCC and a long overdue tank console. 

PRODUCTION FACTS...

The film which took 3 months to complete was shot in Westchester NY during the months of Sept, Oct and Nov of 2022. During that time I acquired 1.15 TB of footage data which then had to be painstakingly edited for well over 200 computer hours. Filmed entirely in 4k res or higher for perfect clarity, the sound was captured and finalized in lossless WAV format. Filmed almost entirely on a Sony A7SIII, other cameras used were Sony A7III, Go Pros for onboard, and DJI drones. Diety and Sennheiser microphones.

snippet.description:
Welcome to 13 WORST Motorcycles From The 1970s, Nobody Wants Back!

For every great bike, there's always one that fails so badly you question how it was approved. These failures have been around since the early days of motorcycles, but they became more common in the 1970s.

It was a time of innovation with parallel twins and advanced triples, alongside the rise of sport bikes in America. 

Join us as we delve into the world of the worst bikes ever made, where ambitious ideas often ended in disappointment and frustration.

snippet.title: JAY LENO'S GARAGE TOUR!
snippet.description:
Jay Leno's Garage is one of the most famous car collections in the world and to be able to visit is incredibly special! Join me with Jay Leno himself for a tour to take in some of the eclectic mix of cars on display as we discover what's within.

Inside the halls lie a huge variety of different automobiles, motorcycles and automotive memorabilia. From modern super and hypercars like the McLaren P1, Porsche Carrera GT, Ford GT and Acura NSX, to the almighty McLaren F1 and legendary classics like the Bugatti Type 35, Jaguar E-Type, Bentleys and Duesenbergs. There is no other collection like it in the world when it comes to sheer variety and to me also the impressive nature of Jay's knowledge about each and every one of them.

Arriving for a visit with my Ford GT, being able to tour around and take it all in has always been a dream, but made even more exciting by Jay joining to show us around himself. Amongst the cars are so many other things to take in and spot lurking around as we explore - I'm sure many hours could be taken to run through everything in detail!

A huge thanks to Jay and the team at Jay Leno's Garage, who you can follow on their channel and Instagram here:
http://youtube.com/jaylenosgarage
http://instagram.com/jaylenosgarage

Thanks for watching, Tim

snippet.title: 1000 Players Build MASSIVE Civilization in Minecraft
snippet.description:
In this video, I put 1000 Minecraft players onto 4 islands, each its own civilization. Each player had the freedom to do whatever they want, but they only had one life. Will there be democracy? Will there be war? Which nations will be triumphant? Find out now!

If you want to play in events like these, join my Discord server:
https://discord.gg/state

More info:
Out of 8000+ applicants, 1200 players were accepted to play in my 1000 Player Civilization Experiment (also known as "Season 2"). Before the event began, players selected which island they wanted to join—plains, desert, snow, or jungle. Each day, all players logged on at the same time, and session lasted around 1-2 hours. For the most part, players could do whatever they want, including mining for resources, running a business, becoming a leader, or fighting in war. We did set a few limitations on the players to promote a better experience, like banning random killing (RDM) as well as disabling most Minecraft enchantments.
DISCLAIMER: While most of the footage and plot information in this video accurately represents what actually happened in this event/experiment, some moments have been modified, reshot, or entirely fabricated for purposes of simplification or storytelling. If you want to know EXACTLY what was real/scripted, or if you just want to learn more about how I made the video, I posted a 3-hour live stream on my "ish 2" YouTube channel explaining the specifics.

Intro - 0:00
Day 1 - 1:11
Day 2 - 4:12
Day 3 - 7:41
Day 4 - 11:53
Day 5 - 14:47
Day 6 - 19:27
Day 7 - 24:06
Day 8 - 30:05
Day 9 - 42:19
Day 10 - 57:49
Epilogue - 1:11:00

#Minecraft #Civilization

snippet.title: 1000 Players Simulate Prison in Minecraft
snippet.description:
In this video, I put 1000 Minecraft players in a massive prison. There were 1000 cells, 100 guards, and 1 warden. Each player only had one life. Will the guards maintain order, or will the prisoners riot and escape? Who will survive? Find out now!

JOIN MY DISCORD SERVER:
https://discord.gg/state

More info:
Out of 4000+ applicants, 1040 players were accepted to play in my prison event. On the first day, players were led from a giant boat into the prison, where they explored their new home. The prison consisted of four large plots where players could build, long hallways with cells and bathrooms, a cafeteria, an infirmary, and the Warden's Tower.
Some prisoners grouped up to cause trouble, while others remained peaceful. Guards functioned within a hierarchy—warden, deputy warden, elite team, prison guard, and perimeter team.
Some of the visuals and audio in this video were recorded after the server ended and are not from the actual event. Additionally, some of the plot information in this video is inaccurate/incomplete for purposes of simplification and storytelling.

0:36 - Day 1
6:43 - Day 2
13:57 - Day 3
19:34 - Day 4
28:46 - Day 5

snippet.title: 100 Players Simulate WORLD WAR 2 in Minecraft Civilization War
snippet.description:
This Soviet City was TURNED TO ASH in this Minecraft WW2 CHAOS... 

Check out my lego channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/@ScotsPlastic/videos
@ScotsPlastic 

Check out my lego podcast: 
https://www.youtube.com/@TheLEGOPodcast
@TheLEGOPodcast 

Thanks to my Minecratf Event Admins:
- StickGolden
- Killerbee47

Thanks to the Minecraft Build Team:
- DKM12
- Djjeezus
- Imperial_Belgium
- Xader (replays) 

🟩 DISCORD:                        https://www.discord.gg/xrJzFwK
🟦 TWITTER:                        https://www.twitter.com/PlasticScot
🟧 INSTAGRAM:                  https://www.instagram.com/plasticscot/

With the success of the previous minecraft ww1 simulation, we wanted to follow it up with not another ww1 minecraft trench war, but the next minecraft war that was supposed to end all all wars... Minecraft world war 2. In this minecraft ww2 simulation 4 minecraft civilizations will compete for control over a minecraft soviet city. The minecraft german reich, the imperial minecraft japanese empire, the union of minecraft soviet socialist republics and the united states of minecraft america. This is a ww2 minecraft obsidian war meaning each minecraft nation will be given a 1 hour build phase, followed by a 1 hour fight phase. Once your obsidian towered is dtreoyed, your team will enter minecraft hardcore mode. Which minecraft civilization will win this world war 2 minecraft simulation? Minecraft usa, minecraft germany, minecraft japan or minecraft soviet union??  
To find out we will not be doing a 100 days in minecraft war, nor will this hardcore minecraft simulation last 100 days, but we do have 100 minecraft players i guess. We had a lot of fun making this minecraft ww2 map and the minecraft ww2 mods really helped bring it to life..

Minecraft WW2 Mod List: 
- WW1_Pack_Addon_v7 - https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/world-war-i-addon/
- viva-la-vida-new-beginning - https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/viva-la-vida-new-beginning-v-1-0/
- WOSWMResourcePack-1.0v
- Invisible World Borders - https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/invisible-world-borders

GAME NAME: Minecraft
GAME LINK: https://www.minecraft.net/en-us
GAME DESCRIPTION: Minecraft is a 2011 sandbox game developed by Mojang Studios and originally released in 2009. The game was created by Markus "Notch" Persson in the Java programming language.

These war minecraft simulation events just keep getting better and better... this time we have the minecraft ussr civilization locked in battle with a minecraft nato civilization. When the fighting starts both the nato minecraft soldiers and the ussr minecraft soldiers will enter hardcore minecraft. That means in minecraft hardcore mode when 1 of the 100 players dies, they don't come back! Let's begin the hardcore minecraft world war 3 battle simulator
Now we have been trying out a few new minecraft civilization simulation events and we're not up to 100 player minecraft war style events. Honestly I think we can get to minecraft 1000 players in a year or two. Each civilization minecraft army will start either side of the berlin wall. When the wall comes down, minecraft world war 3 begins. 
This minecraft ww3 simulations couldn't have been achieved without the minecraft ww3 mods that we installed. But also... the new minecraft animation overhaul mod which we use for clean optifine replay mod cinematics. That mod is incredible so please do check it out. It turns basic minecraft videos and minecraft gameplay into what can only be described as a minecraft cinematic or a minecraft movie. Also we're trying to move away from your average minecraft civilizations war and finding new ways to increase the productions quality of each minecraft video that we make. These teams are all on a minecraft earth multiplayer map where in our minecraft server they are located in the correct geographical position. ~ ~ ~ ~ RULES ~ ~ ~ ~ 
Build Phase
- no scouting other civilizations base
- no stealing
- no killing (unless within the temple)
- no lava traps
- unlimited respawns
- objective is to get loot and fortify 4 obsidian blocks
Fight Phase
- defend your obsidian towers
- destroy all enemy obsidian towers 
- respawns turns off when all obsidian is lost 
- when timer runs out, team with most obsidian wins
- if obsidian is equal, enter sudden death last man standing 

Minecraft East Asia Civilizations War Modpacks
- https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/riki-s-armor-collection/
- https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/varatha-aspect-of-guan-yu/

Recently the Scots Army has been doing minecraft war simulation, minecraft civilization simulation and just any old minecraft simulations if I am honest.. but this minecraft story takes us all the way to the great eastern empires of asia. Today we have the minecraft monglolian civilization, minecraft chinese civilization, minecraft japanese civilization and the minecraft dutch civilization. Using a minecraft earth map we're going to recreate a historical minecraft civilization war between the great asian empires. We start off by doing some incredible historical themed minecraft builds to fortify the spawn points and obsidian towers.. but when the fighting begins this minecraft battle will stop being a minecraft roleplay experiment and will become a minecraft hardcore deathmatch like nothing you have ever seen on a minecraft smp before. So who will win? Minecraft china, minecraft japan, minecraft mongolia or minecraft dutch east indies. Each team has their own minecraft skin and a multiplayer team on this epic minecraft server. Let's see who wins!

~ ~ ~ ~ RULES ~ ~ ~ ~ 
Build Phase
- no scouting other civilizations base
- no stealing
- no killing (unless within the temple)
- no lava traps
- unlimited respawns
- objective is to get loot and fortify 4 obsidian blocks
Fight Phase
- defend your obsidian towers
- destroy all enemy obsidian towers 
- respawns turns off when all obsidian is lost 
- when timer runs out, team with most obsidian wins
- if obsidian is equal, enter sudden death last man standing 

Minecraft East Asia Civilizations War Modpacks
- https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/riki-s-armor-collection/
- https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/varatha-aspect-of-guan-yu/

Recently the Scots Army has been doing minecraft war simulation, minecraft civilization simulation and just any old minecraft simulations if I am honest.. but this minecraft story takes us all the way to the great eastern empires of asia. Today we have the minecraft monglolian civilization, minecraft chinese civilization, minecraft japanese civilization and the minecraft dutch civilization. Using a minecraft earth map we're going to recreate a historical minecraft civilization war between the great asian empires. We start off by doing some incredible historical themed minecraft builds to fortify the spawn points and obsidian towers.. but when the fighting begins this minecraft battle will stop being a minecraft roleplay experiment and will become a minecraft hardcore deathmatch like nothing you have ever seen on a minecraft smp before. So who will win? Minecraft china, minecraft japan, minecraft mongolia or minecraft dutch east indies. Each team has their own minecraft skin and a multiplayer team on this epic minecraft server. Let's see who wins! 

In Minecraft, players explore a blocky, procedurally generated, three-dimensional world with virtually infinite terrain and may discover and extract raw materials, craft tools and items, and build structures, earthworks, and machines.

snippet.title: Whole Earth Radio Sn 2, Ep 12   DSHEA 2.0 w: Ashish Talati
snippet.description:
In this episode, I am honored to address the regulatory future of the Natural Products Industry with Ashish Talati. Ashish and I discuss what is being referred to as DSHEA 2.0.  DSHEA stands for the Dietary Supplement Health Education Act, and it is the law that regulates the production and distribution of nutritional and dietary supplements in the US.
              Ashish R. Talati is one of the industry’s foremost experts on FDA regulatory matters. He has gained an exceptional reputation for his successful results at the cutting edge of FDA and regulatory law, where he has responded nimbly to changes in the regulatory climate and the marketplace, guiding clients through some of our industries’ most complex issues.

Need a DSHEA expert? Please let me highly endorse https://talati-law.com/

As mentioned in this interview, joining industry trade groups is really important.  Please consider joining these groups fighting for the freedom to sell supplements in our country.
PNN https://www.positivelynatural.org/
NPA https://www.npanational.org/
CRN https://www.crnusa.org/
MAHO https://maho4health.org/
SENPA https://senpa.org/
AHPA https://www.ahpa.org/

If there are other industry groups, or others, you think are important please make me aware of them by emailing robseeman@gmail.com

Thank you!
